Program: Omnibus
Title: Jack The Ripper
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p0376jk0
Last Broadcast Date: 20 October 1988
A look at the case of the unidentified serial murderer Jack the Ripper who killed a number of prostitutes in the Whitechapel area of London. Examining the murders and exploring the continuing fascination with the killer in song, plays, films and tourism.